---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BottomDrawer from '../components/BottomDrawer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Blog - Nolan">
  <main class="blog-container">
    <header class="blog-header">
      <h1>Blog</h1>
      <p>Thoughts on technology, innovation, and the future</p>
    </header>

    <div class="blog-grid">
      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/600/300?random=1" alt="The Future of Web Development" />
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-date">March 15, 2024</span>
          <h2><a href="/blog/future-of-web-development">The Future of Web Development: Beyond React</a></h2>
          <p>Exploring emerging frameworks and technologies that are reshaping how we build for the web. From Server Components to Web Assembly, the landscape is evolving rapidly.</p>
          <a href="/blog/future-of-web-development" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/600/300?random=2" alt="AI and Creative Coding" />
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-date">March 8, 2024</span>
          <h2><a href="/blog/ai-creative-coding">AI and Creative Coding: A New Renaissance</a></h2>
          <p>How artificial intelligence is transforming creative expression in code. From generative art to automated design systems, we're entering a new era of digital creativity.</p>
          <a href="/blog/ai-creative-coding" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/600/300?random=3" alt="Building Accessible Interfaces" />
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-date">February 28, 2024</span>
          <h2><a href="/blog/accessible-interfaces">Building Accessible Interfaces That Don't Suck</a></h2>
          <p>A practical guide to creating inclusive web experiences without compromising on design or functionality. Real-world examples and actionable insights.</p>
          <a href="/blog/accessible-interfaces" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/600/300?random=4" alt="The State of CSS" />
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-date">February 20, 2024</span>
          <h2><a href="/blog/state-of-css-2024">The State of CSS in 2024</a></h2>
          <p>Container queries, cascade layers, and new color functions are changing how we style the web. A deep dive into the latest CSS features that actually matter.</p>
          <a href="/blog/state-of-css-2024" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/600/300?random=5" alt="Performance Optimization" />
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-date">February 12, 2024</span>
          <h2><a href="/blog/performance-optimization">Performance Optimization: The Hidden Art</a></h2>
          <p>Beyond Core Web Vitals: advanced techniques for creating lightning-fast web experiences that users love. Metrics that matter and optimizations that work.</p>
          <a href="/blog/performance-optimization" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="blog-card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/600/300?random=6" alt="Design Systems" />
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-date">January 30, 2024</span>
          <h2><a href="/blog/design-systems-2024">Design Systems That Scale</a></h2>
          <p>Building maintainable design systems that grow with your team and product. From tokens to components, creating consistency at scale.</p>
          <a href="/blog/design-systems-2024" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <BottomDrawer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .blog-container {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: white;
    padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .blog-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
  }

  .blog-header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: black;
    text-shadow: 
      -0.1em 0 #ff3333,
      0.1em 0 #33ccff,
      -0.15em 0 rgba(255, 51, 51, 0.8),
      0.15em 0 rgba(51, 204, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .blog-header p {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
    color: #666;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .blog-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .blog-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .blog-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .card-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .card-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .blog-card:hover .card-image img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .card-content {
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  }

  .card-date {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #888;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .card-content h2 {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .card-content h2 a {
    color: black;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card-content h2 a:hover {
    color: #333;
  }

  .card-content p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2vw, 1.1rem);
  }

  .read-more {
    color: black;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .read-more:hover {
    transform: translateX(4px);
    color: #333;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .blog-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .blog-container {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }
    
    .card-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>